Title: Home in the Dream
Description:
Fyrakk has withdrawn from Amirdrassil, but that only increases my concern. He must have another target within the Emerald Dream.

We must convene with the others at the base of the tree. Tyrande and the kaldorei have established a camp. 

I need to speak with Alexstrasza to determine our next step.
ObjectivesText: Meet Merithra at the central encampment beneath Amirdrassil.
